    public abstract class WebdavDirectoryStreamBase<O>
extends DirectoryStreamBase<org.apache.jackrabbit.webdav.MultiStatusResponse,O>
    Base class for webdav directory streams. These streams share some tricky code for getting the file name out of a response, which is now stored in this base class.
